attr.title: Not Tetris 2
attr.desc: A spiritual successor to Tetris in which pieces are free to rotate 360 degrees and have physics applied to them. Originally created by the team at stabyourself.net
attr.inst: Use the d-pad to move your pieces, A/B to rotate. Start is Enter and Select is Escape to navigate menus. To enter high score names, press Start+down on d-pad, up/down left/right to choose letters, and Start to confirm your name. 2 Player mode is not supported
